Package: squaRify
Title: Draw treemaps in base R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Anand", "Mayakonda", , "anandmt3@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1162-687X"))
Description: This package implements squarify treemap algorithm in base R. Main squarify algorithm is a direct translation of python [squarify](https://github.com/laserson/squarify) package by [Uri Laserson](https://github.com/laserson).
